SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT count(*) FROM aktuele_posities A , beleggingsinstrument B , koerskodes C , clienten D WHERE (A.AP_SYMBOOL BETWEEN ~1 and ~2) AND C.KC_LEVERANCIER = ~3 AND (D.CL_RELATIE_TYPE = 1 and A.AP_REKENING_SOORT BETWEEN 100 and 999 OR A.AP_REKENING_SOORT BETWEEN 1 and 99) AND (A.AP_BI_TYPE between 100 and 299 or A.AP_BI_TYPE between 500 and 699 :4) AND (B.BE_SYMBOOL=A.AP_SYMBOOL AND B.BE_OPTIETYPE=A.AP_OPTIETYPE AND B.BE_EXPIRATIEDATUM=A.AP_EXPIRATIEDATUM AND B.BE_EXERCISEPRIJS=A.AP_EXERCISEPRIJS AND C.KC_SYMBOOL=A.AP_SYMBOOL AND C.KC_OPTIETYPE=A.AP_OPTIETYPE AND C.KC_EXPIRATIEDATUM=A.AP_EXPIRATIEDATUM AND C.KC_EXERCISEPRIJS=A.AP_EXERCISEPRIJS AND D.CL_NUMMER=A.AP_RELATIENR)
